{"tid":1713330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要] 陣地防守 特別是中大手足必看！","createTime":"2019-11-12T17:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T01:26:55.000Z","uid":19238,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d50deaaf6437535d36f44d189fb830cff8983cad","tid":1713330,"uid":19238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:05:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 事到如今 有些地方係我地必須防守的 例如各間大學 特別中大 當打陣地戰 手足就必須預計長期抗爭 我有幾個建議 <br />\n第一 <strong>必須安排人輪更休息</strong> 體力很重要!!! 將前線勇武和合理非結合 大概分3更 每更4-5小時自行決定 2更休息  一更放哨和建立防線 一定要安排人做訊息傳遞以防黑警突襲<br />\n<br />\n第二 <strong>強力建議設立指揮部</strong> 讓可以信任的人例如學生會設立指揮部 主要職責包括資訊整理發放 戰術安排 人力資源安排 物資安排 和外界聯繫等 只有合理安排資源才可能打贏這場仗<br />\n<br />\n這絕對是一場長期抗爭 合理有限的物資 和外界交流物資獲取 醫護安排和校方的商討等等才可能保護前線手足安全 !<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！  </span>"},{"pid":"683f5975001f94938b305c841a686c8b5bf1342d","tid":1713330,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a05c661b3e538eeefa358d6c1d49c3364fad971","tid":1713330,"uid":243106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"指揮部好重要，等於人既腦，手腳當然係行動組，手足們，講左咁多個月，終於要堅啪啪上喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4eea35acc9c785e4f5e9b0baaa2a4cb9bade62","tid":1713330,"uid":20689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:11:41.000Z","msg":"休息好重要 前線一定要馬上休息"},{"pid":"36eae2da44b1eb57a90d445a04450446f9ad6bb0","tid":1713330,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"狗宿要人！ 快！<br />\n 圍魏救趙最有效方法 ! <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">攻敵所必救</span></strong></span> !<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1712519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1712519</a><br />\n<br />\n已婚警察宿舍：<br />\n1）青山政府宿舍<br />\n2）柴灣已婚警察宿舍<br />\n3）奥卑利街已婚警察宿舍<br />\n4）黃竹坑警察學院已婚警察宿舍<br />\n5）上水已婚警察宿舍<br />\n6）大欖水警基地幫辨宿舍<br />\n7）青衣已婚警察宿舍<br />\n8）屯門湖康警察宿舍<br />\n9）西區已婚警察宿舍<br />\n10）元朗已婚警察宿舍"},{"pid":"25dd3661c1325362618dd8137ff6c5852eef36b6","tid":1713330,"uid":19238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"Pushhhh 俾前線"},{"pid":"4184ef7c1dacabc479c5f5bd946ea4c0a3014e21","tid":1713330,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c3b3a913d6dc7505abeeec636826fc226ffa7f","tid":1713330,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef99acb09d1ee6d81a14e4d91f88939b3719c4bc","tid":1713330,"uid":19238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:13:49.000Z","msg":"中大學生參考下！！！"},{"pid":"7121a69f7b41aaee681ddfc74bcf79a57f967703","tid":1713330,"uid":42554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:14:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"328c649223bc00e7ebfe862ac72a421fddd907db","tid":1713330,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:14:48.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"ad9db8e3e8ace0df0526eabeca0ec0e18aea0213","tid":1713330,"uid":181649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:15:41.000Z","msg":"推佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e5800dbc3e318aab090764e3ef527c17d11fc5","tid":1713330,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:16:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7e21bd68972